\pard\plain \tx0\tx360\tx720\tx1080\tx1440\tx1800\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\sa360\sl264\slmult1\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Scrivener projects are saved on disk as folders with the extension \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93.scriv\u8221\'94.}
